*.swo
*~

# --- Logs ---
*.log
logs/

# --- Log fixture-recording (ADR-0005 Amendment 2026-05-30, BACKLOG:94) ---
# lib/log.ts can tee logEvent NDJSON to a path when enabled via
# enableFixtureRecording(). Files may contain post-redaction log lines;
# treat as production log output (secret-redaction is best-effort per
# ADR-0005). Default to NOT committing these.
*.ndjson
fixtures/

